### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@serviceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000 
@customerId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@slotId = {{createSlot.response.body.id}}
@bookingId = {{createBooking.response.body.id}}

### 1. Crear Slot de Disponibilidad
# @name createSlot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-02-15T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-02-15T11:00:00Z"
}

### 2. Consultar Slots de un Servicio
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/slots/service/{{serviceId}}

### 3. Crear una Reserva (Booking)
# @name createBooking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "scheduledDate": "2026-02-15T10:00:00Z",
  "slotIds": ["{{slotId}}"],
  "quantity": 1
}

### 4. Obtener Reservas del Cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?customerId={{customerId}}

### 5. Obtener Detalle de Reserva
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}

### 6. Cancelar Reserva
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}
